This tool relies on chromium, chromedriver and the following python3 libraries
pytz tzlocal termcolor selenium requests beautifulsoup4 pygraphml

Installation of chromium via package manager.

Installation of chromedriver:

wget http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/2.14/chromedriver linux64.zip
unzip chromedriver linux64.zip
cp chromedriver /usr/bin/chromedriver
chmod 777 /usr/bin/chromedriver

Installation of python libraries:
pip3 install pytz tzlocal termcolor selenium requests beautifulsoup4 pygraphml


Example: `python3 fb.py -user facebook username`

